        " : قُلْتُ لَهُ اِبْنُ أَخٍ وَ جَدٌّ قَالَ \"اَلْمَالُ بَيْنَهُمَا نِصْفَانِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5647 - Al-Bazanti narrated from Al-Muthanna from Al-Hasan Al-Ṣayqal from Abu Abdullah (as) who said: I asked Imam (as) about a paternal nephew and a grandfather (regarding inheritance).\nImam (as) said: \"The inheritance is divided equally between them, half and half.\""
        ]
      }
